snippet.title: Neuvillette 「Remains Of the Past Day」 Piano "New age style" / Diluvies Chapter Story Cutscene OST
snippet.description:
Genshin Impact - Neuvillette story cutscene 「Remains Of the Past Day」 OST Piano Performance


Today's performance is the ending cutscene of Neuvillette's story quest 'Diluvies Chapter'.
This is the OST inserted into “Remains Of the Past Day”

It is a story quest that is well-received for showing the highest level of perfection, directing, and development of all time.
The content is quite desolate, which makes it even more heartbreaking.
In addition, the original song features string instruments and conveys the sorrowful feeling well.

I follow the flow of the original song, while also focusing on the speed and strength.
I played it in a more sad New Age style.

Thank you for listening.

---------------------------------------------------
Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/TGvwJR9rs7
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano
